On Thu, 16 May 2002, Mike Clark wrote:

> Is there a kit that will convert a generator TO an alternator, whereas it
> looks like the stock generator, but performs as an alternator?
>
> Both my Busses have alternators, but this would be handy for another car (at
> least it is German) that I have.

No, the two operate on completely different principles.  You'd have to
replace all the interior parts of the generator with redesigned bits, and
I think that the diameter of the rotor is important, otherwise VW would
have made the alternator the same size as the generator.

